SPRUITVIEW - Calm has returned to Spruitview in Ekurhuleni after a night of chaos.Residents went on the rampage, setting a truck alight and blocking roads.JHB - N3 Route: #ProtestAction at Spruitview: Truck on fire https://t.co/ALijl1ghCVThey were protesting over electricity cuts, grinding the N3 to a halt.Irate residents vandalised property and looted several shops.Police there were not injuries or arrests but they are investigating a case of public violence.Residents have vowed to continue protesting until their demands are met.eNCA